 trends and valuable technology adjacencies</li>\n</ul>\nThe ipQuants Research Team helps you to better understand the innovation trends and issues that are relevant to your investment strategy. Empower your legal, M&amp;A, business development and strategic planning efforts with insights from the ipQuants Research Team.', 'Research', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '98-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-10-26 21:54:02', '2018-10-26 21:54:02', '', 98, 'https://ipquants.com/98-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
